OL,5, A teacher who filmed himself wrestling 
OL,6, with pupils in "play fights" has been  
OL,7, banned from the profession.            
OL,9,FA panel found Gary Savage had failed to
OL,10,Fobserve professional boundaries at     
OL,11,Fthree public schools in Oxfordshire and
OL,12,FKent in the 1990s, 2000s and 2010s.    
OL,14,FIt said the only reason for filming the
OL,15,Fwrestling could have been "sexually    
OL,16,Fmotivated" and "voyeuristic".          
OL,18,FIt said while he "regrets" his actions,
OL,19,Fhe showed "a lack of insight and       
OL,20,Fremorse".                              
